content: Hello Jeyachandran! Nice to meet you today. I'm Master, and I'll be conducting the technical round of your interview for the Software Engineer position at Google. Before we dive into the questions, I'd like to take a moment to review your resume and get a better understanding of your background and experiences. Can you tell me about your transition from studying Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning at Kongu Engineering College to working as a Web Developer at Fabromant and Centillion Labs? What sparked your interest in web development, and what skills did you acquire during that period?
